    <p>An immersive view into our world of luxury craftsmanship. Explore curated designs, then open Shop or Luxury Handbags to view full catalog and pricing.</p>
  </section>

  <main class="wrap">
    <div class="section-title">
      <div>
        <h2>Curated Visual Collection</h2>
        <p>Browse signature silhouettes and thematic edits. Click any card to preview the concept, or use “Shop” to explore product listings.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="controls">
      <div class="hint" id="countText">Showing 0 items</div>
      <div class="right">
        <input id="searchInput" type="text" placeholder="Search gallery by name, series, or tag..." />
        <button class="btn" id="clearBtn" type="button">Clear</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="grid" id="galleryGrid"></section>

